commit.message:
Row: Allow non-unique column names like sqlite3.Row

* keys method now returns a list of column names which
  are not necessarily unique

* __getitem__ method now returns the value corresponding
 to the first matching column name

* items and values methods can now return multiple items
  or values that correspond to the same key (like multidict)

* __str__ method now inherits the tuple implementation
  since dict requires unique keys

Closes: https://github.com/rqlite/pyrqlite/issues/58
